source: crates/biome_formatter_test/src/snapshot_builder.rs
info: css/scss/declaration/ambiguous-selector-vs-nesting.scss
---

# Input

```scss
.test{
  label:hover{color:red;}
  font:bold{color:blue;}
  font:12px{family:sans-serif;}
  font: bold{family:serif;}
  #{$name}:hover{color:green;}
  a:#{$pseudo}{color:teal;}
  font-#{$weight}:bold{color:purple;}
  font-#{$weight}::before{color:orange;}
}

```


# Formatted

```scss
.test {
	label:hover {
		color: red;
	}
	font:bold {
		color: blue;
	}
	font: 12px {
		family: sans-serif;
	}
	font: bold {
		family: serif;
	}
	#{$name}:hover {
		color: green;
	}
	a: #{$pseudo} {
		color: teal;
	}
	font-#{$weight}:bold {
		color: purple;
	}
	font-#{$weight}::before {
		color: orange;
	}
}

```
